news.title: Noida authority won't allow property brokers in office without passes
news.para: On June 15, OSD Avinash Tripathi issued a letter, saying that many people were found to be unnecessarily visiting various departments of the Authority.

news.title: Chandigarh: IT Park housing scheme of CHB awaits eco-clearance
news.para: The board applied for environmental clearance for the IT Park general housing scheme in February. It got approvals for structure, public health, electrical, town planning and architecture from departments concerned.

news.title: Ghaziabad: UP housing board to slash interest rate on dues of buyers
news.para: The move is expected to benefit homebuyers in Ghaziabad, where the Board is building a township in Sidharth Vihar and plans to construct another in Mandola.
